One of the more valuable contributions of this class has been the thought framework for interviewing and hiring programmers.  
Below I include a series of questions useful in the hiring process.
What version control system do you use?
What unit testing tool do you use?
What framework do you use?
To what alternatives did you compare each of these?
Why each of these and not the alternatives?
What is your GitHub account?
